author: mgrigorov
msg: WICKET-3361 Validation Error on AjaxEditableLabel causes ajax calls in loop on Chrome Browser
Fortify the setting of Wicket.Ajax.baseUrl - use a special getter that returns '.' (i.e. current folder) when the current value is "".
This is needed because if the current value is "" then the request header is not send to the server.
